code: public static char parseSeparator(Settings settings) throws IllegalArgumentException {     String customSeparator = settings.get(SEPARATOR.getPreferredName()).     if (customSeparator == null) {         return DEFAULT_SEPARATOR.     } else if (customSeparator.length() == 1) {         return customSeparator.charAt(0).     }     throw new IllegalArgumentException("Setting [separator] must be a single, non-null character. [" + customSeparator + "] was provided."). }
